One of the reasons I am going to be referring
to them is because (A) they are very good,

00:04:45.790 --> 00:04:50.530
(B) they started to be translated into a number
of languages, and (C) they are available to

00:04:50.530 --> 00:04:54.470
use freely for anybody that is interested
in using them for educational purposes.

00:04:54.470 --> 00:04:59.620
So the Royal Society of Edinburgh and its
the Computing Science curriculum.

00:04:59.620 --> 00:05:01.490
